<div style="text-align:justify;">At the same time, research and development into electrically and nuclear powered vehicles would be stopped by lobbying and governmental intervention. &nbsp;As early as the late 1950&#8217;s Ford had thought of, and planned on developing nuclear powered vehicles. &nbsp;Our own military has used nuclear power for its submarine fleet&#8217;s since the 50&#8217;s as well. &nbsp;If this doesn&#8217;t prove foreknowledge of the catastrophic effects of oil dependence, nothing will.&nbsp;</div>
